This directory contains various text displays:

credits - Shown when a player types 'credits'.
credits.short - Shown during the login sequence.
godlist - Dynamic list of god-level players.
handbook - Immortal rules document on the 'handbook' command.
help - The various help files.
imotd - Shown to immortals when they log in.
info - Newbie guide shown on the 'info' command.
intros - Login screens/greetings.
motd - Shown to mortals when they log in.
names - Name lists for NPCs.
policies - The mortal rules document shown on the 'policy' command.
wizlist - Dynamic list of immortals.
